.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/54563/', '', 'Dextromethorphan, Clofedanol, Benzonatate, Pentoxyverine, Codeine', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Siponimod, Apremilast, More', 1767369485);
